‘‘(ii) any affiliation, agreement, or similar transaction with a foreign
source that involves the use or exchange of an institution’s name, like-
ness, time, services, or resources; and
‘‘(iii) any agreement for the acquisition by purchase, lease, or barter,
of property or services from a foreign source (other than an arms-length
agreement for such acquisition from a foreign source that is not a for-
