PURPOSE
To amend the Higher Education Act of 1965 to require additional
information in disclosures of foreign gifts and contracts from for-
eign sources, restrict contracts with certain foreign entities and for-
eign countries of concern, require certain staff and faculty to report
foreign gifts and contracts, and require disclosure of certain foreign
investments within endowments.
